ActFederal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the Federal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS UNDER THE FEDERAL-PROVINCIAL FISCAL ARRANGEMENTS ACT, in order to clarify definitions used for the calculation of Territorial Formula Financing (TFF) and to clarify definitions used for calculations and reflect legislative changes to the Federal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act for the Canada Health Transfer (CHT).
